include ../../mixins/toolbar.jade

md-content.full-content(layout="column" flex)
	+toolbar("Donate")
	md-content(layout='row')
		div(layout='column')
			include ../../partials/left-side-nav.jade
		content(layout='column' flex)
			md-content


				.padding-standard
					h2 Donation Impact

					p ineedtotalk.org provides free support group services to anyone in the world. However, there are a lot of moving pieces involved, ranging from server uptime, to encryption costs, to content creation, and graphic design.

					p Your donation will go towards sustaining our support group services, and allow the business to expand. Future plans include:

					ul
						li iOS and Android applications
						li A database for local crisis centers and shelters
						li Private messaging
						li Audio/video integration
						li Case work services
						li Mobile crisis units
						li Internationalization

					p In order to leave a donation, You may click the PayPal button below.

					h2 Dedication

					p Any donation of at least&nbsp;
						b {{vm.dedicationAmount}} {{vm.dedicationCurrency}}
						span &nbsp; will allow you to dedicate your donation to a loved one. All dedications can be viewed&nbsp;
						a(sref="dedication-list") here.
						span &nbsp; If you would like to leave a dedication, then leave your email address as a note in your donation.

					img(src="/public/shared/img/donation-email.png" style='max-width:100%;')

					p
						b Please note: you must use an email address associated with an ineedtotalk account in order to leave a dedication. If you need to modify the email address of your dedication, you may contact &nbsp;
							a(href='mailto:support@ineedtotalk.org') support@ineedtotalk.org
						span . After completing your donation, you will receive an email with details on how to create a dedication.

